Package: chromeR
Type: Package
Title: Visualizing IBD Segments on Chromosomes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Richard Munoz
Maintainer: Richard Munoz <rmunoz@cs.columbia.edu>
Description: chromeR provides two functions, one for calculating the lengths
    of shared IBD segments and lengths not shared (gaps) and another function that
    takes that output and provides an example plot.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, tidyr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
